{"tid":1643150,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"記憶能力與情緒研究","createTime":"2019-10-10T03:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T08:46:49.000Z","uid":316556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c89e845f4b6f5d758e87b3ab33b453ccad1ea428","tid":1643150,"uid":316556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"各位你好，我是香港城市大學心理學碩士生，感受到近月來大家既情緒深受影響，唔開心、失望、絕望、悲痛、憤怒、抑鬱，我而家做緊關於記憶能力與情緒的研究既FYP，我希望可以在處理情緒方面既研究可以做出D貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n如你年滿18歲，誠邀你完成本問卷，將不勝感激。 您的資料將保密，僅用於學術研究（已過ethical review）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeYYlmNRfMQaa1lZWnkZr-XE5p4Enrc0ASBXUr4k-As_bjZmQ/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeYYlmNRfMQaa1lZWnkZr-XE5p4Enrc0ASBXUr4k-As_bjZmQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=e4874acc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeYYlmNRfMQaa1lZWnkZr-XE5p4Enrc0ASBXUr4k-As_bjZmQ/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n感激"},{"pid":"174ef7a685f88dec53735c091206a63770d8660b","tid":1643150,"uid":58174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:11:45.000Z","msg":"個post好似少咗啲嘢wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353e2776bc83524f59bb6ae333eacde4f91a5116","tid":1643150,"uid":97113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:12:58.000Z","msg":"j"},{"pid":"86e5169685c911469cb3dda2c23c23932d957d29","tid":1643150,"uid":307712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"識唔識規矩"},{"pid":"5fd900704114a2bee0027bc540a5b3f7521b95c7","tid":1643150,"uid":16985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"識唔識規距"},{"pid":"78e3a8b3698c8e5b109ff431234e0378b5a41a56","tid":1643150,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:32:38.